 Proto watched as the bot statred to absorb the other.  He couldnt let it 
happen tyhe bot was too strong. He ran at the bot. The boit turned to him and 
grabbed him by the throat. His fire energy cut throughhim easily. He openened 
his mouth and ate the bot thats when the cacoonm surronded. So now Galvatron 
was getting two for the price of one. The lights from the cacoon birghtened 
and brigthened. Till it could be seen a mile away. No doubt the fighters at 
the cf took notice due to the 1/2 mile distance they where from the base.
